      <div class="item item8">
        <img src="cards.jpg" alt="Project 1">

        <p>For this project, the specification was to make a list that displays
         one random card from each card suit. I did this using JavaScript to create this
        fun little game. My partner covered the second half
       where the player gets assigned a random number and has to guess it to win.
      To get new values for both, the page needs to be refreshed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item item9">
        <img src="roots.jpg" alt="Project 2">

        <p>This is a screenshot from a website I made for a company called Roots Garden
         Center. Here you can see the about page where the company's founder and leaders
        are highlighted. It covers some of their accomplishments and helps visitors to the site
      understand what Roots is all about.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item item10">
        <img src="panini.jpg" alt="Project 3">

        <p>This project was for a food truck. The owners wanted to
         include the times and places where the truck would be visiting each week.
        They also asked to include the different events they stop at throughout the year.
       I showcase this through a table under the events page. This is a screenshot of the
      welcome page.</p>
      </div>

