      <div class="item item11">
        <img src="war.jpg" alt="Project 4">

        <p>This is a website version of the classic card game war. To play, the players
         hit play and a card is chosen for each from any of four suits. The player
        with the highest card value wins. If the cards are the same in value, there is a tie.
       At the end of the round, the players are asked if they want to play agian.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item item12">
        <img src="yogi.jpg" alt="Project 5">

        <p>This is a website I made for YogiBear State Park. The park rangers really
         wanted to get more people involved in their activities and nature reserve program.
        To do this, I used a gallery and plenty of images to showcase the beauty and amenities of the
       park. This is from the home page.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item item13">
        <img src="hawaii.jpg" alt="Project 6">

        <p>Hawaii has many activities and opportunities for tourists. A company
         specializing in recreational activities reached out to me to design their home page.
        I focused on using a beach-toned color scheme and images to draw visitors in. Their top
        attractions are included on the front page as well.</p>
      </div>

